b3a20e0c   * the SubAgentTool factory accepts.
64e75266   *
873d95ed   * Returns `{}` (empty record) when the block is missing or `enabled !== true`.
02a8da19   * Throws `PersonaLoadError` on any validation or path-traversal failure.
533a9f11   */
